description:
Riley Keough, Sam Claflin, Suki Waterhouse and more star in Daisy Jones & The Six, now streaming on Prime Video.

About Daisy Jones & The Six: In 1977, Daisy Jones & The Six were on top of the world. Fronted by two heat seeking missiles in Daisy Jones and Billy Dunne, the band had risen from obscurity to fame. And then, after a sold-out show at Chicago's Soldier Field, they called it quits. Now, decades later, the band members finally agree to reveal the truth. This is the story of how an iconic band imploded at the height of its powers.
